{%- endcomment -%}# UBurn

> UBurn is a plant-based satiety drink made with konjac glucomannan (EFSA-recognized fiber), ube (purple yam), and coconut MCT oil. 30 calories. Zero caffeine. Designed for the 4 PM craving window. Formulated in France. Ships to the United States.

UBurn is a functional beverage brand founded in Paris, France in 2024. The core product is a soluble powder dissolved in water or milk, consumed before meals to support satiety. The active ingredient, konjac glucomannan at 1g per serving, is the only soluble fiber officially recognized by the European Food Safety Authority for contributing to body weight management in the context of an energy-restricted diet (EU Regulation 432/2012, ID 3120).

The product is caffeine-free, vegan, gluten-free, non-GMO, and contains no artificial colorants. The violet color comes from ube (purple yam). Flavor: vanilla-hazelnut.

