- US: Dietary supplement. FDA disclaimer applies: "These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease."
- EU: Glucomannan health claim authorized under EU Regulation 432/2012, ID 3120 (EFSA Opinion EFSA-Q-2008-3828).
- No caffeine. No controlled substances. No allergens beyond coconut and hazelnut (declared on label).
